run(sql="
with cte as(
    select distinct b.pogId, 
                    count(distinct case when a.orderDate>='2023-05-04' and a.orderDate<='2023-05-11' then a.subOrderId end) as SD_DS, 
                    count(distinct case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' and  a.orderDate>='2023-05-04' and a.orderDate<='2023-05-11' then a.subOrderId end) as FB_DS, 
                    count(distinct case when a.orderDate>='2023-06-05' and a.orderDate<='2023-06-12' then a.subOrderId end) as SD_DS_now, 
                    count(distinct case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' and  a.orderDate>='2023-06-05' and a.orderDate<='2023-06-12' then a.subOrderId end) as FB_DS_now 
    from `temp.final_attri2` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
    on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
    group by b.pogId
    order by SD_DS desc
    LIMIT 100
),

cte2 as(
    select distinct b.pogId, count(distinct case when a.orderDate>='2023-05-04' and a.orderDate<='2023-05-11' then a.subOrderId end) as SD_DS, sum(c.nm) as SD_NM, sum(case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then c.nm end) as FB_NM 
    from`temp.final_attri2` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
    on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
    left join `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)` c 
    on a.subOrderId=c.subOrderId
    where a.orderDate>='2023-05-04' and a.orderDate<='2023-05-11'
    group by b.pogId
    order by SD_DS desc 
    LIMIT 100
)

select distinct cte.pogId, 
                cte.SD_DS/8 as SD_ADS, 
                cte.FB_DS/8 as FB_ADS, 
                cte2.SD_NM, 
                cte2.SD_NM/cte.SD_DS as SD_NMSO, 
                cte2.FB_NM, 
                cte2.FB_NM/cte.FB_DS as FB_NMSO, 
                b.NMSO as predicted_NMSO, 
                cte.SD_DS_now/8 as SD_ADS_now, 
                cte.FB_DS_now/8 as FB_ADS_now
from cte left join cte2
on cte.pogId=cte2.pogId
left join `temp.pnm1` b 
on cte2.pogId=b.pogId   
order by SD_ADS desc
",1000)
